caters to high net worth individuals and pension and profit sharing plans it manages separate clientfocused equity fixed income and balanced portfolios the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe it also invests in alternative investment markets including precious metals currencies energy commodities reits variable annuities and structured products the firm invests in mutual funds and exchange traded funds for the equity portion of its portfolio it primarily invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified sectors for the fixed income portion of its portfolio the firm invests in diversified portfolio of investments including government bonds high yield bonds marketlinked certificates of deposit municipal bonds investmentgrade domestic bonds shortterm reserves foreign bonds and inflationprotected bonds it employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios the firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the sp  index canterbury volatility index wide moat focus index msci usa catholic values index and msci kld  social index it employs a combination of inhouse and external research to make its investments brookstone capital management llc was founded in  and is based in wheaton illinois detailed description  south naperville roadsuite wheaton il united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwbrookstonecmcom key executives for brookstone capital management llc mr dean zayed jd llmcfp president and chief executive officer mr darryl ronconi chief operating officer mr mark w diorio cfa chief investment officer mr derek gubala national director of business development mr matthew lee lovett chief compliance officer compensation as of fiscal year  brookstone capital management llc key developments brookstone capital management llc presents at morningstar etf conference  chicago  sep  am aug   brookstone capital management llc presents at morningstar etf conference  chicago  sep  am v